  HTML5, CSS3, HTTP
end note

note right of presentation
  **Tecnologías:**
  Thymeleaf, HTML, CSS
end note

note right of web
  **Tecnologías:**
  Spring MVC, Servlet API
end note

note right of service
  **Tecnologías:**
  Java 21, POJOs
end note

note right of infrastructure
